videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Weatherspoon excites the crowd with a huge block, then Robert Woodard II scores on a putback on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Weatherspoon's block leads to Miss State's transition layup) 2020/01/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Weatherspoon's block leads to Miss State's transition layup

videos.description: J'Von McCormick sets up an alley-oop with Anfernee McLemore but the dunk is no good, then McCormick hustles for the loose ball and scores.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's McCormick follows up alley-oop miss) 2020/01/04 ESHEET
